graph TB
    subgraph "Kubeflow Trainer Operator"
        Controller[trainer-controller-manager<br/>Go Controller]
        Webhook[Validating Webhooks<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        TrainJobCtrl[TrainJob Controller<br/>Reconciler]
        RuntimeCtrl[TrainingRuntime Controller<br/>Reconciler]
        ClusterRuntimeCtrl[ClusterTrainingRuntime Controller<br/>Reconciler]
        ProgressTracker[Progression Tracker<br/>RHOAI Extension]
        NetworkPolicyMgr[Network Policy Manager<br/>RHOAI Extension]

        Controller --> TrainJobCtrl
        Controller --> RuntimeCtrl
        Controller --> ClusterRuntimeCtrl
        Controller --> ProgressTracker
        Controller --> NetworkPolicyMgr
        Controller --> Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        TrainJobCR[TrainJob CR<br/>Namespaced]
        TrainingRuntimeCR[TrainingRuntime CR<br/>Namespaced]
        ClusterTrainingRuntimeCR[ClusterTrainingRuntime CR<br/>Cluster-scoped]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        JobSet[JobSet<br/>Multi-node training]
        PodGroup[PodGroup<br/>Gang scheduling]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Pod isolation]
        TrainingPods[Training Pods<br/>GPU workloads]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|kubectl apply| TrainJobCR
    TrainJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    TrainJobCR -->|watched by| TrainJobCtrl
    TrainingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtrl
    ClusterTrainingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| ClusterRuntimeCtrl

    TrainJobCtrl -->|creates| JobSet
    TrainJobCtrl -->|creates| PodGroup
    NetworkPolicyMgr -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    JobSet -->|creates| TrainingPods

    ProgressTracker -->|polls /metrics| TrainingPods
    ProgressTracker -->|updates annotation| TrainJobCR

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
        JobSetController[JobSet Controller<br/>v0.10.1]
        VolcanoScheduler[Volcano Scheduler<br/>v1.13.1 Optional]
        PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>RHOAI]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/creates| K8sAPI
    JobSet -->|managed by| JobSetController
    PodGroup -->|scheduled by| VolcanoScheduler
    Controller -->|exposes metrics| PrometheusOp

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job queueing]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Secure communication]
        Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>PodMonitor]
    end

    TrainJobCtrl -.->|managedBy field| Kueue
    TrainingPods -.->|optional| ServiceMesh
    Controller -->|metrics via PodMonitor| Monitoring

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style ProgressTracker fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style NetworkPolicyMgr fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style TrainJobCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style JobSetController fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style VolcanoScheduler fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Kueue fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
